Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.19,0:02:52.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,昨天发生的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.55,0:02:55.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,维甘袭击事件的后续报道
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.40,0:02:57.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,军方发言人宣称
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.74,0:03:02.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,本次袭击事件中无人伤亡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.26,0:03:06.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 关于维甘机动战士的入侵途径
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.17,0:03:07.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,据称还在调查中…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.80,0:03:10.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到处都在说这件事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.98,0:03:14.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没办法 维甘攻来了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.28,0:03:15.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过就算他们再来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.95,0:03:18.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那台白色机动战士也会把他们打回老家
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.99,0:03:20.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.55,0:03:22.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可惜啊 亚瑟姆
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.23,0:03:24.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.86,0:03:27.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没赶上昨天那场战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.21,0:03:29.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,场面可大了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.32,0:03:30.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊…嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.66,0:03:34.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,话说 从没见过那种白色机动战士
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.48,0:03:35.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是军队的新机型吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.87,0:03:37.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.98,0:03:44.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亚瑟姆 千万记住
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.47,0:03:47.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你驾驶高达的事要绝对保密
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.09,0:03:49.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.33,0:03:52.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,维甘的目标恐怕是高达
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.81,0:03:54.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白其中的含义吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.53,0:03:57.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.63,0:04:00.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亚瑟姆知道什么吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.96,0:04:03.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没 不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.78,0:04:05.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你老爸是军人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.86,0:04:08.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有小道消息吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.71,0:04:11.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉 老爸只字未提
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.23,0:04:12.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.46,0:04:13.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 罗玛丽
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.88,0:04:23.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是不是想加入我们社团了…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.75,0:04:24.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.03,0:04:30.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是来为昨天的事道谢的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.23,0:04:32.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 关于那件事…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.82,0:04:35.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道 要保密是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.28,0:04:36.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是我们俩的秘密
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.83,0:04:39.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 加油
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.67,0:04:41.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,期待比赛那天
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.75,0:04:43.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.22,0:04:49.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这家伙 什么时候勾搭上的？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.46,0:04:51.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没…没什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.73,0:04:53.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道吗 青春就是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.74,0:04:55.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,友情和恋情和机动战士
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.95,0:04:58.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.13,0:04:59.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里有友情
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.00,0:05:01.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也有机动战士
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.67,0:05:03.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只差恋情了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.43,0:05:05.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在说什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.19,0:05:07.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反正明白就是了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.42,0:05:09.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过我也有同感
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.04,0:05:11.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.27,0:05:12.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亚瑟姆
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.63,0:05:15.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的青春从此开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.03,0:05:17.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.22,0:05:32.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然联邦军进行了情报管制
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.79,0:05:33.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是通过战斗发生的位置
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.97,0:05:35.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和现场残留的痕迹
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.77,0:05:40.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们已经圈定了高达的所在区域
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.11,0:05:41.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是这里
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.68,0:05:52.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.10,0:05:53.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想必你也知道
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.89,0:05:56.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是以锻造机动战士闻名的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.28,0:05:58.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明日野家族的私人宅邸
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.54,0:06:00.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亚瑟姆的父亲是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.14,0:06:03.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,地球联邦军总部巨环基地司令
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.47,0:06:05.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原高达驾驶者
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.47,0:06:06.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样说来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.79,0:06:10.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,高达被藏匿在亚瑟姆家的可能性极高
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.57,0:06:16.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只换轴承果然作用不大…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.92,0:06:21.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是说 我也想加入机动战士社团
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.16,0:06:23.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上次自己说没兴趣的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.09,0:06:26.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏威 有什么关系
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.18,0:06:29.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一定可以帮上你们的忙
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.86,0:06:45.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,了不起 太厉害了 杰哈特
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.57,0:06:48.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,程序稍作调整就变化这么大
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.64,0:06:50.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,切 没办法
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.43,0:06:53.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧 允许你加入
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.46,0:06:58.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,离大会不远了 请多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.14,0:07:02.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.60,0:07:04.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,彼此彼此
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.55,0:07:27.55,INCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}翻开相册 装着你我的笑颜
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.02,0:07:34.94,INCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}率真的双眸中 有同样的梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.66,0:07:43.54,INCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}沾满泥巴的双手 仿佛忘记时间的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.69,0:07:52.90,INCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}过去的岁月 至今不失光彩 对吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.02,0:07:57.45,INCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}飞逝的时光一角
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.00,0:08:01.30,INCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}只属于你我的课后
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.40,0:08:09.42,INCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}率真的净土 永远记得
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.74,0:08:18.39,INCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}那一瞬是真实 你与我同在
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.47,0:08:24.34,INCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}彼此信赖…毫无虚假
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.85,0:08:33.41,INCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}感叹过往时光
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.77,0:08:48.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别硬掰 夏威
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.03,0:08:51.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弄坏的话就前功尽弃了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.21,0:08:54.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别…担心 就好了…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.93,0:08:56.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.74,0:08:59.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,罗玛丽！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.54,0:09:04.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,危险
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.91,0:09:13.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.85,0:09:15.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.50,0:09:17.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小心点 夏威
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.90,0:09:19.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.66,0:09:21.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思 罗玛丽
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.14,0:09:22.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 我没事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.71,0:09:26.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就说加点机油吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.16,0:09:44.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,需要的零件全在这里了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.10,0:10:05.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,似乎略显疲态
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.34,0:10:06.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.53,0:10:08.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,调查的进展如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.77,0:10:10.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是 除一个地方以外
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.98,0:10:13.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们已经搜遍了整个地区
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.44,0:10:15.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,结果和之前相同
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.09,0:10:16.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一个地方？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.24,0:10:17.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明日野家
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.79,0:10:22.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,高达就藏在明日野家里
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.89,0:10:24.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这点确信无疑
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.45,0:10:27.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是那里警卫森严…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.47,0:10:28.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.69,0:10:31.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这件事交给我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.12,0:10:32.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你确定？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.79,0:10:33.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.85,0:10:35.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.22,0:10:43.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我来这里不是为做这种事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.04,0:10:45.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,必须赶紧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.53,0:10:47.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为实现维甘的夙愿
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.03,0:10:51.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去我家？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.29,0:10:55.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 你父亲是巨环基地的司令吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.67,0:10:59.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,家里有很多机动战士的相关资料吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.57,0:11:02.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有是有 但那是爸爸的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.60,0:11:04.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能随便给别人看
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.52,0:11:06.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想想办法吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.56,0:11:11.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说不定能找到提高性能用的珍贵资料
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.52,0:11:12.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.88,0:11:14.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了变得更强 亚瑟姆
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.86,0:11:15.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.90,0:11:17.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不想在比赛里获胜
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.38,0:11:19.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让老爸见识下吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.24,0:11:23.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧 可以
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.06,0:11:26.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,事后再向父亲道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.46,0:11:28.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这也是为了让我们的机体变得更强
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.00,0:11:30.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.29,0:11:31.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这才是亚瑟姆
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.98,0:11:33.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过别乱翻哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.06,0:11:35.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道的
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,//---------------------------------TXTB------------------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.30,0:11:43.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打扰了～
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.10,0:11:45.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欢迎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.55,0:11:49.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们去下父亲的书房
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.31,0:11:51.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可以乱碰里面的东西哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.87,0:11:53.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.32,0:11:54.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.23,0:11:55.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,失礼了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.59,0:11:56.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.22,0:12:01.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一群有意思的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.46,0:12:03.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个长发的人好帅
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.96,0:12:04.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.74,0:12:05.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.75,0:12:14.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不愧是巨环基地司令的房间
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.06,0:12:19.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,机动战士相关的书是这本…这本
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.73,0:12:27.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杰哈特？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.46,0:12:30.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊… 我去厕所
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.66,0:12:33.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沿着走廊 到底右拐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.80,0:12:35.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.79,0:12:44.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这幢房子不像能藏得下机动战士啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.67,0:12:46.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 剩下的可能性…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.73,0:13:10.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,终于找到了 高达
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.47,0:13:15.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这一天终于到了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.45,0:13:17.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,机动战士模拟格斗大赛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.76,0:13:21.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,托尔迪亚的年轻技师们齐聚一堂
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.93,0:13:24.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,装配机动战士和负责操纵的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.99,0:13:26.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全部是学生
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.28,0:13:28.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们的智慧 热情
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.30,0:13:30.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即将在此碰撞出炽热的火花！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.20,0:13:37.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们的愿望只有一个
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.33,0:13:40.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,战斗 获胜 夺冠！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.94,0:13:43.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是48支队伍中
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.44,0:13:46.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能够如愿以偿的只有一队
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.91,0:13:51.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,究竟是哪支队伍最后胜出
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.42,0:13:54.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,获得荣耀的桂冠呢！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.70,0:13:56.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.74,0:14:01.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.05,0:14:12.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下一场就是决赛了 亚瑟姆
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.77,0:14:14.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杰哈特呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.46,0:14:15.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.82,0:14:17.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才就一直没看见他
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.18,0:14:33.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白 计划按时开始
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.52,0:14:35.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也会马上前往汇合
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.64,0:14:47.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,另一支进入决赛的队伍出现了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.62,0:14:49.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哈特曼校队
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.58,0:14:52.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,驾驶者是法比·德鲁斯缇
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.33,0:14:54.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别拍对手队伍了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.58,0:14:56.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快给亚瑟姆镜头
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.35,0:14:59.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凡格斯大人 那是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.90,0:15:18.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什…什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.91,0:15:21.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,距离决赛开始不到5分钟
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.99,0:15:24.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杰哈特干什么去了？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.73,0:15:28.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种时候什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.71,0:15:29.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.86,0:15:31.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好了 亚瑟姆
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.28,0:15:33.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,维甘的机动战士又来了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.18,0:15:38.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 你去哪 亚瑟姆
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.92,0:15:40.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,决赛马上开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.33,0:15:42.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉 这里拜托
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.92,0:15:44.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.92,0:15:47.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我们怎么办？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.47,0:15:50.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亚瑟姆？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.00,0:16:11.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快回来 亚瑟姆
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.43,0:16:14.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们虽然在迎战 但坚持不了多久
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.41,0:16:16.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.33,0:16:23.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.63,0:16:26.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能再去了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.44,0:16:29.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们拦不住敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.23,0:16:38.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.65,0:16:45.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小小的麻烦 但无碍大局
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.32,0:16:49.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.88,0:16:55.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶 趁我不在
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.14,0:17:07.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亚瑟姆
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.32,0:17:08.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开火 开火
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.57,0:17:13.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶 又来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.72,0:17:19.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 趁现在
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.20,0:17:31.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶的维甘
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.55,0:17:44.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卑鄙无耻
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.16,0:17:48.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然是亚瑟姆
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.44,0:18:15.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那家伙呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.35,0:18:18.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上面吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.11,0:18:22.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,胜负已分了 高达
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.51,0:18:26.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不算什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.29,0:18:41.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶 大意了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.07,0:18:43.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,速战速决
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.55,0:18:48.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这家伙哪来的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.34,0:18:49.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,援兵吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.69,0:18:54.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杰哈特大人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.21,0:18:57.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凡格斯大人 情况不妙
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.46,0:18:59.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道 再等会
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.06,0:19:04.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 设定完成
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.26,0:19:05.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尝尝这招
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.62,0:19:22.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到哪里去了 高达
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.22,0:19:30.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.20,0:20:06.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不会杀你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.77,0:20:08.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是得给我老实点
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.46,0:20:15.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亚瑟姆
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.31,0:20:24.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么会在这里？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.87,0:20:32.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,危险 罗玛丽
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.20,0:20:33.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快离开这儿
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.30,0:20:45.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,联邦军的机动战士
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.36,0:20:47.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶 拖延太久
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.41,0:21:04.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,逃走了…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.50,0:21:08.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亚瑟姆
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.64,0:21:17.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,结果大会改期了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.26,0:21:21.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没办法 据说维甘又来进攻
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.58,0:21:25.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过 还是被那台白色机动战士打回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.70,0:21:27.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这次没看到
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.05,0:21:29.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.24,0:21:32.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了 亚瑟姆和杰哈特呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.02,0:21:35.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天他们请假
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.20,0:21:37.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.81,0:21:47.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里是菲利特麾下的联邦军设施
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.57,0:21:51.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把高达藏在这里可以放心
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.12,0:21:54.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别担心 菲利特会保护我们
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.21,0:21:55.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不论遇到什么敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.99,0:22:00.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,高达被运出明日野家
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.68,0:22:03.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,目前去向不明
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.10,0:22:04.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.27,0:22:05.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,达乌内斯总部下令
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.62,0:22:10.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,继续潜伏直至成功夺取高达
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.33,0:22:11.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.24,0:22:14.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就这样
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.04,0:22:23.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么我刚才松了一口气？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.94,0:22:26.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么我…
